Package: nicerplot
Type: Package
Title: Create NiceR Plots and Save them as Png/Pdf/Jpeg/Svg
Version: 2022.4.12
Authors@R: person("Martijn", "Dijkstra", email = "m.dijkstra@cpb.nl", role = c("cre","aut"))
Description: Create elegant data visualisations and save them in high resolution png or pdf. Input can be an xlsx-file, a CBS-url, a data frame, a list, a matrix, or a time-series (mts, ts) object.
